      <title>基辅寻求武器支持，泽连斯基派特使前往首尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/zelenskiy-sends-envoy-to-seoul-as-kyiv-seeks-weapons-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰国防部长鲁斯泰姆·乌梅罗夫正在韩国进行访问，外界普遍认为此行旨在寻求韩国的武器供应，以帮助基辅击退目前得到朝鲜支持的俄罗斯入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/zelenskiy-sends-envoy-to-seoul-as-kyiv-seeks-weapons-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 09:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
